            <title><![CDATA[Kyoto Xanadu official trailer, second TV commercial]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/07/kyoto-xanadu-official-trailer-second-tv-commercial</link>
            <guid>1565578</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Featuring the theme song "From 'i'" by LinoN.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><a title="Companies > Nihon Falcom [771 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/nihon-falcom">Falcom</a> has released a two-minute trailer and new TV commercial for <em><a title="Games > Kyoto Xanadu [9 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/kyoto-xanadu">Kyoto Xanadu</a></em>, featuring new gameplay cuts and the theme song “From ‘i'” by in-game virtual singer <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2026/02/kyoto-xanadu-details-masayuki-rikudo-shu-kadenokoji-toushu-and-linon">LinoN</a>. The theme song is also available now to download or stream via music services like mora, music.jp, Spotify, Amazon Music, Apple Music, and YouTube Music. <span id="more-1062000"></span></p><p><em>Kyoto Xanadu</em> is due out for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [11,514 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [1,049 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [18,382 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/4449410/KYOTO_XANADU_the_Blooming_Phantom/" target="_blank">Steam</a> on July 16 in Japan and Asia. A western release is also planned.</p><p>Watch the trailer below. View a new set of screenshots <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/gallery/kyoto-xanadu/july-1-2026/">at the gallery</a>.</p><h2><span>Trailer</span></h2><p><strong>Japanese</strong></p><p><iframe title="『亰都ザナドゥ -桜花幻舞-』プロモーショントレーラー" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/X07XarRB2bw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><!-- AD: content -->
        <p><strong>Korean</strong></p><p><iframe title="『교토 재너두 -앵화환무-』 프로모션 트레일러 #교토재너두" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/v_H-NJsW6w8?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Traditional Chinese</strong></p><p><iframe title="《亰都幻都 - 櫻花幻舞 -》宣傳預告片 #亰都幻都" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/kFExd8AwNbU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Simplified Chinese</strong></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="《亰都幻都 - 樱花幻舞 -》宣传预告片 #亰都幻都" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/1kth8d7Yp6k?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><h2><span>TV Commercial #2</span></h2><p><strong>Japanese</strong></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="『亰都ザナドゥ -桜花幻舞-』TVCM 第二弾" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ddqpFLCoMF0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Korean</strong></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="『교토 재너두 -앵화환무-』 15초 WEB CM 제2탄 #교토재너두" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/_RrhbU5KLhE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Traditional Chinese</strong></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="《亰都幻都 - 櫻花幻舞 -》第二波15秒網路廣告 #亰都幻都" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/NJfi2Rt8Gio?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Simplified Chinese</strong></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="《亰都幻都 - 樱花幻舞 -》第二波15秒网络广告 #亰都幻都" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Qk1Buk_XpZs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><h2><span>Screenshots</span></h2><div id="carousel_1062001"><ul><li><span>❮</span></li><li><span>❯</span></li></ul></div></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/07/kyoto-xanadu-official-trailer-second-tv-commercial]]></content:encoded>
